name: Chiaroscuro
description:
While illuminated and seemingly alive, the forest is simultaneously consumed in darkness.

Like the Orchid Matis that lures in its prey with its beauty. The forest is beautiful and deadly.

As you move closer, you begin to notice the overwhelming amount of branches that are poised to stake themselves into any unconscious victim who may have been lulled by the enchantment of the chemiluminescent put off by the overgrowth.

Like many things in life, this forest is beautiful but deadly. Because beautiful is dangerous.
